"title": "5437: palaces",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5437: palaces",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Fortified, luxurious residences for kings. They normally served as the seat and symbol of royal authority.</p>\n<h2>David's palace on Mount Zion</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:1\">1CH 14:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:6-2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:6–5:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:4-1Chr11:8\">1CH 11:4–11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:1-2Sam7:2\">2SA 7:1–7:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:1\">1CH 17:1</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's palace in Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:4-1Kgs10:5\">1KI 10:4–10:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:3-2Chr9:4\">2CH 9:3–9:4</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:1-1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:1–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:16-1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:16–10:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:15-2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:15–9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:11\">2CH 8:11</a></p>\n<h2>Gold and valuable items were stored in the palace in Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18-1Kgs15:19\">1KI 15:18–15:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2-2Chr16:3\">2CH 16:2–16:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:25-1Kgs14:26\">1KI 14:25–14:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:17-2Kgs12:18\">2KI 12:17–12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:13-2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:13–14:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:23-2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:23–25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:7-2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:7–16:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:20-2Chr28:21\">2CH 28:20–28:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:14-2Kgs18:15\">2KI 18:14–18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:16-2Chr21:17\">2CH 21:16–21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:18-Jer27:22\">JER 27:18–27:22</a></p>\n<h2>The royal palace in Jerusalem was destroyed by the Babylonians</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:9\">2KI 25:9</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:19\">2CH 36:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:13\">JER 52:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:1-Jer22:6\">JER 22:1–22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:8\">JER 39:8</a></p>\n<h2>Other palaces</h2>\n<h3>The kings of Israel had palaces in Samaria</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1\">1KI 21:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:5-1Kgs20:6\">1KI 20:5–20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:43\">1KI 20:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:25\">2KI 15:25</a></p>\n<h3>Foreign palaces</h3>\n<p>Pharaoh's palace in Egypt:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:15\">GEN 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:40\">GEN 41:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:14\">GEN 47:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:3\">EXO 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:29-Dan4:30\">DAN 4:29–4:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:9\">EST 1:9</a> <em>King Xerxes' palace in Persia and Media</em></p>\n<h3>Summer palaces</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:20-Judg3:21\">JDG 3:20–3:21</a></p>\n<h2>Palaces in NT times</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:3-Matt26:4\">MAT 26:3–26:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:28\">JHN 18:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:35\">ACT 23:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:12-Phil1:13\">PHP 1:12–1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Features of palaces</h2>\n<h3>Palace gardens</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:18\">2KI 21:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:25-2Kgs21:26\">2KI 21:25–21:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:5-Esth1:6\">EST 1:5–1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The luxury of palaces</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:39\">1KI 22:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:18\">NUM 22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:8-Ps45:9\">PSA 45:8–45:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">ISA 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13-Jer22:17\">JER 22:13–22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:8\">MAT 11:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:25\">LUK 7:25</a></p>\n<h2>Palaces were administered by royal officials</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:5\">2KI 10:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:6\">1KI 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:3\">1KI 18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:5\">2KI 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:7\">2CH 28:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:15\">ISA 22:15</a></p>",
